# mailbox-send

Use this skill for any agent-authored mailbox entry. Prefer it over manually editing `mailbox/MAILBOX.jsonl`.

## Before first use

Read `mailbox/README.md`.

## Command

Single-line message:

```bash
uv run python skills/mailbox-send/scripts/send_mailbox.py --task-id <task_id> --message "Need decision on next step."
```

Multi-line message from stdin:

```bash
cat /tmp/message.txt | uv run python skills/mailbox-send/scripts/send_mailbox.py --task-id <task_id>
```

## Rules

- One mailbox entry per distinct update or request.
- Keep messages concise and decision-oriented.
- The script only appends new JSONL entries; it never rewrites old lines.
